	(1, '[URGENT: Read up]\r\n"Hi, TDF. I have no choice but to seek help from you. Do you know anyone from MBB? I badly need to find a friend of mine from Omegle who happens to be a part of batch 2013, an AHS alumnus and is currently taking MBB right now. The last time we talked, he was bidding his goodbye at me for he might kill himself on 4th attempt this time. I\'m doing this just to seek for peace of mind. I just want to know of he is still safe and that\'s it. Thank you and please notice this message."\r\nMr MBB student, your friend\'s looking for you. If you wanna reach this friend, please, please send us a private message.\r\n- Lisbon'),
	(2, 'Pwede bang magcolorcoding tayo sa Tuesday Red for Taken (stop), Yellow for Confused (not yet or getting ready) and Green for (Go lang Ganern) at hindi tayo nagsasayang ng energy sa panglalandi ng mga taken pala hahahaha - Ate East'),
	(3, '"In defence of the Paminta Guy,\r\nApparently, even in UP, many guys who are still in the closet are being berated by those who are out. We\'re being attacked for apparently not staying true to our colors. For not being comfortable with public showing about how ""fabulous"" we are. For not having a lisp. For our discreet hookups and underhanded momols.\r\nI don\'t stand in solidarity with the rest of the out and proud gay guys. YOU perpetuate stereotypes. YOU, with your loud demeanor and ""Oh I\'m excused from being rowdy coz I\'m gay and comfortable with that!"" mentality. YOU who claims to be the ""true"" representative of the ""gay cause"".\r\nYou think UP Babaylan is the haven for the LGBT? Guess again. How many ""paminta"" guys do you have there? Zilch. Because they effin\' discriminate even within the community.\r\nI am gay but I am not fab. "\r\n-Lois, 2014, Science'),
	(4, 'sardinespsychubermed\r\n"please TDF post this asap huhu i dont want to lose this person\r\nWe were supposed to meet at 9pm again pero hindi ko alam bakit minamalas ata ako at hindi ako makapunta kung san dapat tayo maguusap. I\'ll leave this to you instead. Hindi ko talaga maaccess. Puro error :( please understand that I cant go to you right now\r\nDear sardinas,\r\nI admire you for your strength and I\'m just in awe of how you are handling your life right now. I don\'t fully know your struggle. I don;t have the slightest idea of how much work you\'ve been doing, how many hours you\'ve been spending on doing extras in order for you to reach your dreams. I admire your passion to be the best doctor you can be, heck you totally got out of your comfort zone just to pursue your goal and it inspired me a lot, seriously. I just can\'t explain how amazed I am by your composure, your persistence and your dedication to your goals. I don\'t exactly know how you\'re doing but I am sincerely hoping for best for you, that you will live up tp every single dream you have right now.\r\nI know that I am practically a stranger to you right now, but as I\'ve mentioned, I\'m willing to be that ""person"" to you without asking for anything grand, or almost anything at all. I just want you to know that I will be here for you if you want me to. I know how it feels when the stuff around you is overwhelming and it drowns you with tiredness, fears etc. and sometimes, you just need someone to hold onto. Someone who will listen to your thoughts, who genuinely cares for you. Who\'s honest and who\'s eager to help you in every way that she can. If you need that someone, i\'m here. You know, i always want to find someone who\'s just one text away or one call away or one chat away. Someone who will immediately respond to you if something;s wrong o someone who will celebrate with you when something great happened or simply, someone who you can splurge your randoms thoughts to. Someone who will give you constructive criticisms. Someone who will offer her shoulder for you to lean onto. Someone who will never judge you for your choices.\r\nwhen you need someone. Anything you want from that someone, just tell me and I will defy whatever it is to be there for you. i know you are a strong person and I know that you have every ability to surmount all the challenges that you face in your life. i know you are intelligent and i know you will go far but when things are too much for you and you just need a friend to comfort you, I\'m just here. I don\'t know what\'s in it for me, honestly. I am not even asking for anything from you. I actually just want you to know that I know how it feels when you think that you are alone in your battles and it never ends. And that the whole day you just feel tired from everything and you just want to let out all your angst. All your anger, all your pain. I know how it feels, to be alone, to be sad and in those moments, I always wished there was someone who will just be there. Who will listen. who will give me advises of what I should do. Who does not have to anything at all actually, just someone who will hold on to you when you feel like the waves of life are crashing down on you. I always wished there was that someone. And if you ever wished for someone to be there for you, I;m here. Remember that\r\nIf you have an emergency. If you feel sad. If you feel talking to me. Feel free to chat and message me. Take your time if you still can\'t. I will understand if you are too afraid to try. Whenever it is, I will be there."\r\n-shiftee, 2015, Arts and Letters\r\n\r\nLikeShow more reactionsCommentShare\r\nChronological\r\n23 23\r\n1 share\r\n1 Comment\r\nComments\r\nBudz Casila\r\nBudz Casila ang ganda ng message nya Bam Ba\r\nLike 路 Reply 路 1 路 February 23 at 2:57pm\r\nReginald Recario\r\n\r\nWrite a comment...\r\nChoose file\r\nStatusPhoto/Video\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWrite something on this Page...\r\n\r\nTDF - Kwentong UP Diliman\r\nMarch 5 at 10:36am 路 \r\n[URGENT: Read up]\r\n"Hi, TDF. I have no choice but to seek help from you. Do you know anyone from MBB? I badly need to find a friend of mine from Omegle who happens to be a part of batch 2013, an AHS alumnus and is currently taking MBB right now. The last time we talked, he was bidding his goodbye at me for he might kill himself on 4th attempt this time. I\'m doing this just to seek for peace of mind. I just want to know of he is still safe and that\'s it. Thank you and please notice this message."\r\nMr MBB student, your friend\'s looking for you. If you wanna reach this friend, please, please send us a private message.\r\n- Lisbon'),
	(5, 'Alex Kabigting\r\n"Hello Alex!\r\nSince February na at ilang taon na rin, I just wanted to say na thank you at crush kita. Ikaw ang unang napansin ko sa mga girls sa EEE pagka-shift ko. Thank you sa pagbibigay sa akin ng ngiti tuwing panahon ng paghihirap sa dept. Thank you for being an inspiration to me. Hindi ko alam kung kilala mo ako but yeah, I\'m just one the many faces na dumadaan sa may 2nd floor. Tuwing nandun ako at nandun ka, binabagalan ko talaga paglalakad para lang mas masilayan ka. AFAIK you have someone na and hindi rin naman ako umaasa since I\'m not into commitments pa LOL. Hanggang tingin-tingin lang, appreciating the art of nature. I hope that you guys stay strong for a long time.\r\nStay gorgeous!"\r\n-ZynTax, 2013, Engineering'),
	(6, 'KUYANG UP PEP DRUMMER\r\n"(TDF help your kapwa iska HAHAHA. Sana mapost siya sa FB page huhu ????)\r\nHello kay kuya drummer na nagturo sa CHL 7-9AM class namin last Monday (01/30/17 to be exact lol) :) Ang cool mo! Huhu baka marami nang nagsabi sayo nito pero sobrang cutie mo hehehe specially habang nagtuturo ka ng mga cheer.Motivated na ako umattend ng games omg sana lagi kita makita.\r\nSadly, I don\'t know your name.\r\nI remember you wearing a black ""utak at puso"" shirt that day. May fab ka rin na side bangs, medyo matangkad and may braces. (GUYS KUNG KILALA NIYO SIYA HELP ME WANTED PO SIYA HAHAHAHA CHAROT).\r\nHi lang ulit and ang cutie mo talaga :D\r\nP.s. YEHEY MAY PICTURE KA NA (siya yata yung nasa rightmost part ng 2nd row [from the bottom]) HELLO HELLO TO YOUUUU ????\r\nP.p.s. First time ko humingi ng tulong sa TDF wooooh yesss help me know his name tysm love you peeps :D"\r\n-SOPHIA, 2015, Social Sciences and Philosophy'),
	(7, 'Hi Xandi!\r\n"Lagi kitang napapansin sa may basement. So yeah, member ako sa isa sa mga orgs dun, to narrow down, yung org namin isa sa mga lumipat sa basement. Poker face lang ako tuwing dumadaan ka pero deep inside gusto kong magtatatalon sa tuwa. You complete my day kasi.\r\nHindi ko alam kung ano nagustuhan ko sa iyo. Yung fact na super active ka sa CSSP? Your pretty face? Your smile? O lahat? Basta one day I realized na crush na pala kita. I know you\'re taken na, and I\'m happy for you.\r\nI don\'t think magpapakilala ako anytime soon, not unless siguro org matters na baka pumapel ako para lang makausap ka hahaha. So ayun, good luck sa endeavors mo sa buhay! Always be happy dahil may mga taong ayaw na nakikita kang malungkot!"\r\n-(Not my real College), 2013, Fine Arts'),
	(8, 'Hello Cash!\r\n"Hindi ko na maalala kung paano ko nalaman yung name mo pero tumatak ka talaga sa akin. Ang ganda mo lalo na kapag nakangiti, nakakahawa. Wala akong masyadong alam tungkol sa iyo but I hope that one day, we can get to know each other. Yun ay kung maglalakas loob ako na lapitan ka. We had a brief encounter before sa 42 nung nag-sit in kayo sa class namin kaso occupied tayo nung lab so hanggang silip lang ako sa station niyo. I\'m willing to teach you hahaha pero seryoso, crush man kita o hindi, I\'m willing. Balita ko may BF ka, I don\'t know if it\'s true but I hope inaalagaan ka niya.\r\nSo kung hindi pa rin obvious, CRUSH kita. :)\r\nAlways wear that smile on your already beautiful face!"\r\n-SegFault, 2013, Engineering'),
	(9, 'Gab Lahoz\r\n"Gab,\r\nI don\'t know why I love you. I never thought I could feel this feeling again after a very long time. Thank you for making me realize that I could fall in love again. Thank you for allowing me to have you by my side. Thank you for those candid moments we shared together. Thank you for your thoughtful words that healed my heart.\r\nThank you for making me fall in love again. If you know who I am, please don\'t change. I\'m not yet ready to be hurt once again. "\r\n-Thanks, 2015, Social Sciences and Philosophy'),
	(10, 'Konrad Magboo\r\n"Wag ka na sumama sa kanya. Sa akin nalang. (char) UP Fair tayo tara.\r\nBio:\r\n5 ft but not taller than 5\'3 so magiging matangkad ka :)\r\nCan be funny\r\nNever-ending memes\r\nDefo not a yandere\r\nDefo pun master\r\nDefo not Elaine :)\r\nWon\'t ask for food (if manlilibre ka go lang :))\r\nYou know me naman\r\nNot a benzene but knows toluene\r\nMay be tsundere at times (but will not punch you swear)\r\nI\'m g all the time\r\nSo ano na? Tara UP FAIR. IWAN MO NA SIYA PAGLALARUAN KA LANG NIYA.\r\nP.S. Gusto ko sana ipakita yung picture natin sa CS Audi kaso hiya ako masyado :(("\r\n-Slightly tsundere, 2015, Science'),
	(11, 'PARA SA BOYFRIEND KONG ANTUKIN\r\nSanay na kong ikaw lagi nauunang nakakatulog satin. Almost every morning may ""Sorry natulugan nanaman kita :("" akong nababasa (hindi ako galit ha hehe bc sleep is lyf)\r\nPero kasi may isang gabi na medyo SPG usapan natin (iykwim ????) tapos tinulugan mo ko aba walanjo. Aanuhin mo ko tapos ano. Ikaw pa nagsimula tapos tutulugan mo ko walangya ka ????\r\nAnyway haha mahal pa rin kita kahit ilang beses mo ko tulugan uli :----) baka habang binabasa mo to nakatulog ka pa ha nako talaga. Labyu ???? tulog ka na uli.\r\nperam college. mwa.\r\nb, ****, CVM'),
	(12, 'To my sis na may pseudonym Kill, I understand what you are feeling towards our org. As a woman, naiinis din ako sa mga brods at sisses natin na kumampi pa sa asshole na yun(that\'s right, may sisses). Biased din ang failed trial natin because his friends are the one who is leading our meetings. It\'s more like na mas inemphasize pa nila ang performance mo in our activities than the incident itself, mas binibigyan pa ng time ang ibang topics then wala nang oras to talk about that issue. Pero sabi mo sa amin na ang higher office na ang magreresolve ng issue, pero bakit nagpapakita pa rin ang asshole na yun sa tamb natin and nakakapasok pa siya? Wag mo din isipin nasa side kaming lahat sa asshole na yan, the reason na sumasama ako sa kanila ay para sa tsismis and para marinig side nila at malinaw sa akin na sila ang may mali. Sorry if I never showed publicly my support to you to the reason na ayokong majudge ng orgmates natin and makarinig ng unpleasant words about sa akin like what happened to the other members. Everytime na nakakasama ko si asshole, nagiiba ang statements niya that\'s why I voted to impeach him. I even want to expel or suspend him sa org pero sabi ng ibang brods and sisses ""Bakit expulsion? Hindi naman sa org ang kasalanan niya, sa member"", so ilang incidents pa na katulad nito ang hihintayin natin para marealize mo na affected ang org sa incidents na ganito. For some na nagvictim blaming pa, ""Bakit kasi naglasing pa?"", are you even listening to the story? Pumunta na siya sa room niya and pinuntahan siya ni asshole. To the brods na may lakas pa ng loob na magjoke sa tamb about that issue, may sis po sa paligid niyo, konting respect lang po. It is clear to me na ang parameters for judgment ninyo is how close you are not the offense itself. Right now, tbh, super welcome pa si asshole sa org like nothing happened and ikaw pa ang napasama.\r\nMake it Double Kill, 2016, CEAT'),
	(13, 'ara po to sa lahat ng nagdodorm or apartment na may kasama sa bahay, hindi sa nilalahat ko kayo or anything ha pero ..\r\nHindi ba talaga kayo marunong mahiya? Or tinuruan man lang ba kayo sa bahay ng simpleng manners? Gaano ba kahirap ilagay sa lababo yung mga plato na ginamit nyo at hugasan after kumain or kapag may vacant na kayo? Or tumayo man lang kapag magtatapon ng basura kesa ilapag mo dyan sa table and makita mo one week after sa sulok sulok.\r\nI AM SICK AND TIRED OF CLEANING UP YOUR MESS GUYS. Hindi ako OC or what sadyang gusto ko lang nakakagalaw ako ng maayos sa apartment at hindi parang anytime na umalis ako sa bed may kung anong maapakan na ko sa lapag, like that SPOON from last night or damit nyo na pakalat kalat. Tapos ang bukang bibig nyo ""Kaya mo na yang linisin"" Putangina lang ano dahil nasanay kayong naglilinis ako talagang pinanghawakan nyo na ako talaga laging maglilinis? Be considerate naman. Hindi ako makaalis kasi I still consider you guys as my friends pero hindi na kayo mga bata para maging alagain pa, to think na graduating na kayo ha (Oo delayed ako) pero ganyan pa din kayong umasta.\r\nPlease sa mga walang pakielam kung makalat gamit nyo or sa mga balahura na may kasama sa dorm punyeta mag solo na lang kayo at nakakaperwisyo kayo. \r\nMind your own business nga di ba? Pero be responsible enough naman.\r\nAtengPagodNgUmintindi, 2015, CFNR'),
	(14, 'I entered an organization years ago. I met people and called and treated them as brothers and sisters. Inabot ko yung times na matututo ka ng iba\'t ibang games din pati inom. Super family yung feeling. DATI. Iba na kasi ngayon. Karamihan sa kanila di na ko nagtitiwala. There was an incident na I was sexually harassed kuno ng brod ko. Learned it from another brod. Kasi kinwento niya (asshole to brod) and hinihipuan ko din daw siya. Like, wtf, was too drunk to the point na first and last scenes lang naalala ko. Pero naalala kong nasa stomach ko hands niya paggising ko, pero pinagsawalang bahala ko yun (that was so wrong).Nagtake action naman ako regarding the matter pero may change of plans na naganap. So bakit nadamay tiwala ko sa org? Kasi for most people, all I felt was apathy, tang-ina pamilya my ass. I had an orgmate pa na ang sabi is ""bakit inopen mo sa org, nawalan tuloy ng tiwala ang sisses sa brods"". Ang gusto ko lang naman i-point out rito for everyones sake eh BASIC RIGHT PO ANG PAGRESPETO SA ISA\'T-ISA, ORGMATE OR NOT, ANUMANG GENDER, RESPETUHIN NATIN LAHAT NG LIVING CREATURE HOY. (P.S. I wrote this down kasi I had a dream of the asshole again tapos binabato ko siya ng empty glass in my dreams :)))\r\nKill, 2016, CEAT'),
	(15, 'Pag ako naprovoke magnenamedrop na ako ng org. Tangina magFRA kayo wag kayo puro hingi. Di yan makatarungan sa aplikante. Tandaan nyo walang org kung walang members. Tapos ganyan nyo tratuhin yung \'future members\' nyo? Kung makahingi kayo kala nyo may patago kayo ah.\r\n2k Magic in the Air, 15, BSA, CA\r\n(Admin note: ILAGLAG MO NA!)'),
	(16, 'Curiosity kille dthe cat.\r\nPakalat-kalat yung journal/diary ni roommate sa dorm. Alam kong journal/diary nya yun kasi one time na nagliligpit ako ng room, nakita ko yun and looked inside kasi akala ko sakin. Only to find out na sa kanya pala at may mga journal entry. \r\nOne time, dahil bored ako (plus nakakatemt talaga), medyo binasa ko sya. Nung una, okay pa. Inspirational kumbaga. May mga bible verses pa. May ilan din na about this guy na common friend namin. Turned out, she has a thing for him pala! Isinulat nya mga sweet moments na nafeel nya pag kasama si guy. Medyo kinilig naman ako. At the same time, naawa ako kay ategirl kasi halatang friendzone sya kay kuya. Yes. You heard it right. babae nafriendzone ng lalaki.\r\nHere\'s the shocking part. I discovered (thru her journal) na may nangyari na sa kanila ni guy! I was really shocked kasi conservative si ate. ""True love waits"" pa nga ang motto nya e. At eto pa. Sa room namin mismo nangyari! One night na di ako dun natulog! Ewan kung pano nya naipuslit si kuya. Pero she wrote it down in details how everything led to that. At ngayon, I can never look at them the same way again. Lagi kong napipicture sa utak ko yung mga sinulat ni ate sa journal nya.\r\nPara kay ate, sorry po, nabasa ko yung little secret mo. Pero ate, tigilan mo na po. Friendzone ka talaga eh. Sayang di ka nakapag wait nang mas matagal. You don\'t deserve someone as manhid as him.\r\ntjciwy, 2015, CAS'),
	(17, 'Admin ipost mo to please! Tangina e\r\nEdi eto tangina, sumasali yung girlfriend ko sa isang org. Syempre susuportahan ko kase yun yung org na matagal nya na gusto salihan. Maramihan daw yung pagrerecruit this time, in short mass rec. Kesyo ganito daw dadalian yung process at wala daw finals and shits. Pero ang matindi after presentation, kailangan nila makaipon ng 2k each sa buong process (1-2 weeks). Oo bes tama, 2k each! Nag-init yung tenga ko nung narinig ko. Isipin mo kung ilang aplikante ang meron sa mass rec tapos 2k each? Tangina di ko matanggap. Dalawa org ko pero kahit kailan di ako/kami hiningan ng 2k para lang maging member. Lakas manghingi ng 2k e akala mo naman kabilis lang kuhanin ng pera. Tangina paregconize muna kayo sa OSA. Time!\r\n2k Magic in the Air, 15 , BSA, CA'),
	(18, 'To the boy who keeps on saying that he likes me but doesn\'t show:\r\nI know you don\'t read Elbi Files but I am still hoping that this message would reach you. Besides, I think your ex or your girlfriend does. At least she\'ll know.\r\nI\'m confused. Sabi mo break na kayo ng girlfriend mo. Grad na siya pero madalas pa rin siya bumisita sa Elbi at madalas pa rin kayong magkasama. Sabi rin ng intelligence unit ko, kayo pa. Pero ang sabi mo naman ay friends lang kayo? Pero may post siya sa Instagram nya about sayo nung sinamahan mo siya sa isang event. Sabi mo wag ako mangamba kasi ayaw naman sakanya ng orgmates mo or nung friends mo. Ayaw mo rin sakanya dahil sabi mo iba siya. Dahil sorority girl siya at party girl siya before. Enough ba yun?\r\nDinadahilan mo pa na kung kayo edi sana may picture kayo together sa facebook mo. E hindi ba nature mo na as a person na maging sobrang private? Ang dami dami mong tinatago. Yung privacy settings ng FB mo malupit. Pati ang dami mo pa dinadahilan, bakit hindi pa tayo mag DTR? Gawa ng parents mo sabi mo. Minsan sinasabi mo gawa ng acads. Pag sinasabi ko naman na wag nalang kaya, ayaw mo naman bumitaw. Pwde bang linawin mo na sakin ang lahat? Or at least sakanya linawin mo na ang lahat. Kasi naguguluhan na ko. Malay mo siya rin naguguluhan na sa kilos mo. Di ka ba nahihirapan magtago? Ang gulo mo lang. Parang gusto mo ko na ayaw mo.\r\nAno ba talaga ako sayo ha? Di ako makapag focus sa acads ko kasi tangina lang. Set me free para naman makakilos ako.\r\nPeram ng info mo! Para naman may clue yang girlfriend mo na ikaw ang tinutukoy ko.\r\nMigraine, 2014, BSCE, CEAT'),
	(19, 'Please lang wag niyo na itorment pa lalo ang friend ko. Alam niyo kung sino kayo. \r\nKung gusto ng isang studyante na mag-quit sa org hayaan niyong mag-quit. Hindi pare-parehas ang tolerance ng mga tao. Kung kayo ay \'malakas\' at kayang mag-take ng ganung pang-gagago, hindi ibig sabihin niyun ay ganun din ang iba. \r\nMeron pang ibang members niyo na narinig kong sabi nila ay ayaw sa gago, kupal, at pisikal na kupal pero ngayon tinotorment din ang friend ko. UP students kayo, wag kayong ganyan. Wag kayo yung tipong porket hindi kaparehas niyo or agree sa ideas niyo ay gagaguhin niyo. May Human Rights din ang mga studyante. \r\nWag niyong piliting mag-stay sa org niyo yung kaibigan ko kahit ayaw niya na. Wag ganun.\r\nHypocritesSaHumanRights, 2014, CAS'),
	(20, '[March 7, 2017, 12:50 AM]\r\nShout out lang dun sa isang grupo ng mga estudyante na maingay habang kumakain sila sa labas ng McDo, tapos pagpunta nila sa may gate ay nagsisigaw sila don na parang tanga hanggang umalis na sila (around 10:30 to 11:00 nangyari).\r\nAnong mga problema niyo sa buhay? Bakit kayo umaalulong sa McDo at bakit kayo nagsisisigaw nang sobrang lakas at paulit-ulit ng ""Wooooo"" sa may gate? Nakadrugs ba kayo? Social experiment? Parte ng initiation? Katuwaan lang? Naghahanap lang ng sakit ng katawan? Gustong mapaos para hindi muna mag speech sa SPCM? Gusto niyo lang mambulabog sa dis-oras ng gabi?\r\nAware naman kayo na may mga nag-aaral sa mga katabi niyong table nung nag-iingay kayo, diba (sabi nung isa sa inyo, ""uy may mga nag aaral"")? And please wag niyong sabihing ""public place yan, magagawa nila gusto nila. wala naman kayo sa library, wag kang entitled."" Ano ba naman yung common courtesy, diba mga bes?\r\nBago niyo rin ako sabihan ng ""sana sinaway mo na lang kung tingin mong ikaw ang nasa tama"", hindi ako prepared makipag-away tonight. Exams first. Sa ibang linggo na lang, pag umulit sila ng kanilang kakaibang gawain na yon. \r\nSo ayon, di ko alam kung pano tatapusin to. Ge.\r\ndisturbedindividual, 2013, CPAF'),
	(21, 'PARA SA GAGO KONG EX,\r\nHOY ULOL. SANA MABAOG KA NA NO? SO \'YANG BAGO MONG GIRLFRIEND NA PINALIT MO SAAKIN, \'YANG ""THE ONE"" NA SINASABI MO, \'YAN YUNG SINASABI MONG ""FRIEND"" NA HINAHATID MO LAGI SA DORM NIYA DIBA? KAHIT NUNG TAYO PA? KAHIT NUNG KAYO PA NUNG EX MO? DIBA? GAGO KA PALA EH.\r\nSABI MO YOU WERE UNHAPPY WITH OUR LDR ARRANGEMENT PERO PUTANG INA LAKAS DIN NG UHAW MO NO?\r\nSO ANO KAMI NUNG EX MO, PAMPALIPAS GUTOM. UHAW NA UHAW KA GANON KAYA KAMI MUNA HANGGA\'T DI KA PA SINASAGOT NYANG BABAENG POKPOKITA NA \'YAN NA DI KA MALAYU-LAYUAN KAHIT MAY GIRLFRIEND KA. BUT FOR ALL I KNOW HINDI NYA ALAM NA MAY GIRLFRIEND KA KASI HIYANG HIYA KA NAMAN SAAKIN DIBA?\r\nMABAOG SANA KAYONG DALAWA MGA HAYOP NA PUNYETA. TANGINA GALIT AKO HAYOP KA. KALA KO TOTOO YUNG TAYO. KALA KO MINAHAL MO TALAGA AKO. TANGINA WILKINS LANG PALA AKO. PAMPATANGGAL UHAW PANSAMANTALA.\r\nALL THIS TIME I WAS LOOKING FOR AN EXPLANATION. TANGA KO FOREVER FOR BELIEVING IN YOU. I WISH I NEVER MET YOU.\r\nPERFECT ILLUSION , 14, CAS'),
	(22, 'Para sa bestfriend kong jinowa yung ex ko. Tang ina mo alam mo yung bro code? Tigang na tigang ka ba?\r\nPara dun naman sa ex ko sabi mo ayaw mo muna ng relationship kaya mo ako iniwan. Ano yan? Tapos sa bestfriend ko pa. Trip niyo ko?\r\nTang ina niyo mag bbreak din kayo mga pakyu\r\nMas malaki padin tite ko sayo gago, 13, Bsbio, CEM'),
	(23, 'Kuyang Osu! player sa Mineski,\r\nPutang ina naman pre, pakidahan-dahanan naman yung pagkalampag mo sa keyboard. Nararamdaman namin sa table yung bawat pindot/hampas mo. Eto yung tipo ng tao na walang pake sa effect sa ibang tao ng actions nya, nightmare room/dormmate siguro to. Madalas ka maglaro sa MI, kahit di kita nakikita alam kong nandun ka kasi ramdam ko yung Kalampag Aura mo, puta ka.\r\nKung sino nakakakilala dito pakisabihan na lang in private na wag syang gago maglaro. Pumupunta tayo dun para mag relax for a while, pero mas naiistress ako dahil sayo.\r\nYung mukha mo kasi, mukhang mang-aaway kaya di kita masabihan in person. Oo, duwag na kung duwag pero maawa ka naman sa mga katabi mo. Yun lang.\r\nTime.\r\n22 per hour, 2013, CAS'),
	(24, 'Para sa inyo na ginagamit ang org para sa pandaraya, tangina lang.\r\nNakakaproud siguro ang magtopnotch for the first time at sa isang sobrang hirap na exer pa noh? Hindi lang \'yun, naperfect mo pa. Grabe kuya, galing mo! Binati ka pa ni sir kasi napaka-unusual daw na may makaperfect sa exer na \'yun kasi sobrang hirap nga pero kuya, nagawa mo! Congrats sa\'yo! Kahit hindi ka nagpuyat para mag-aral, kahit an hour before ka lang nag-review sabi mo, nagawa mo pa ring mag-100 na score, iba ka! Kaya pala naman ganoon kaiksi lang \'yung span ng pagrereview mo ay dahil mayroon ka na palang alam sa exer, katunayan nga alam mo na pala buong exer at may solution ka na rin. Kaya pala iniiwas mo sa akin yung ""reviewer"" mo noong tumabi na ako sa\'yo kasi mismong sagot na pala \'yun. Haha. Nalaman ko \'to kasi tangina din daw sabi ng orgmate mo. Tangina daw na pinerfect ng isang mokong. Bakit mo daw sinaulo, baka daw mahalata kasi bopols ka naman daw kaya tangina! Nasaan na honor mo? Nasa UP ka pa naman na may motto na ganoon. Pero tangina lang din naman ng orgmate mong nagpicture ng tanong at solution nila noh?! Tangina na kalat na pala sa org niyo \'yan kaya pala \'yung iba mong orgmates ay chill lang din sa pag-eexer at nasa top din habang ito akong walang tulog, nagkamali pa rin. Di naman ako nagrarant kasi di niyo sinabi sa akin. Ang akin lang, wag ka na sanang proud kasi wala ka bang konsensya? Dinaya mo, kuya! Dinaya mo! Tangina! Alam na \'yan ng lahat! At wag na wag mo kong sasabihan na mag-org na rin kasi ako, hinding-hindi ko gagamitin ang org ko para sa mga kadayaan tulad ng ginagawa niyo sa org niyo. Tangina niyo! Awardees pa man din \'yung iba sa inyo, \'yan pala paraan niyo. Tangina lang!\r\nNot your friend anymore, 2013, CAS'),
	(25, 'Best Friend\r\nOne week before Valentines, I bought you a cake because it was your birthday. I love you very much then, (I haven\'t bought a cake for my mom yet).\r\nValentines day. I saw you that morning and you asked me where\'s your rose from me and I answered, ""ako ba dapat magbibigay?"". then the night comes, I am still thinking if i\'ll buy you a rose and ask someone to give it to you after your \'fellowship\' but i decided not to because I think going to that \'fellowship\' is much better gift than rose. I eventually texted you if you\'ll attend or not, but you didn\'t replied. I also used someone\'s number to greet and text you a Happy Valentine and also say I Love You.\r\nWe both attended the \'fellowship\'. After the \'fellowship\', our different groups went to the freedom park to do our businesses, and after doing my business, I went to join your group since one of your groupmates is my friend.\r\nWhen we\'re together, it was my first time to feel that treatment you gave me. You\'re so cold and I never felt that. So I decided to go home instead of staying up all night with you.\r\nI even texted you that it would be last time joining that \'fellowship\' but you didn\'t reply.\r\nWednesday evening. I saw you sitting on one of the benches near mariang banga, but I did not go to you, instead I sit near you and wait for my friend (he\'s your friend also) without letting you notice (though i didn\'t know if you noticed me). and then my friend came. when we were about to go to the fair, she noticed you and your housemate. she greeted both of you, and I did the same. Your housemate greeted us also, and you only greeted my friend. Then we went back to our business, we went to the fair, while we were on our way, she told me that she noticed that you were looking at me coldly. I just smiled at her.\r\nThursday evening. I texted you using different number to know whether you\'ll reply or not because you did not reply with my texts using my number and you replied. I asked you to meet me 9:30-10:00 and you said you\'re not sure if you\'re still available. Time had passed and it was already past ten, I was calling you back then, once, twice, thrice? it took me 7 times to call you. but you didn\'t answered me.\r\n12 mn. I decided to join my friends. We went to LB Square. It was just my second time drinking alcohol. Unlike my first, I didn\'t let myself get drunk. Because I know there\'ll be no change on how you will treat me.\r\nFriday, Saturday, Sunday, Monday had passed and you\'re still as cold as ever.\r\nTuesday afternoon. I saw you walking going to your classroom and we\'re on the same way so I decided to walk faster so that I can catch up with you.\r\nI asked you that afternoon, why. You just told me, ""wag mo ng intindihin yun, okay lang yan"" and it left think that you already knew that I Love You.\r\nAfter that afternoon. I can\'t think that I\'ll be able to talk to you again. And now, I am missing you. I miss the way we talk. I miss the days I can make jokes and fun of you. I miss you my dear best friend.\r\nMernels, 2015, CEAT'),
	(26, 'I\'m Drunk, I Like You\r\nThat night was when of all my heartaches ended, or so I thought.\r\nNagpakalasing ako that night kasi wasak ako, lalo na yung puso ko. Nagmahal kasi ako ng maling tao. Mali kasi kaibigan ko, mali kasi alam ko namang hindi niya ako magugustuhan, at mali kasi alam kong iba ang gusto niya.\r\nAng gusto ko lang naman noong gabing yun ay maka move on na sa kanya. At dahil sayo, nagawa ko yun. Pero tangina, sayo naman ako na-fall.\r\nYou were a stranger to me that night. Inintroduce ka lang sakin nung isa kong barkada. Di ka naman kagwapuhan, pero ewan ko ba, I find you cute. During that moment, that was all. Na-cute-an lang talaga ako sayo. But why did you have to take care of me when I was already drunk af?\r\nBakit mo ako kinausap? Bakit mo tinawag nang paulit-ulit ang pangalan ko to the point na na-inlove na ako sa boses mo? Bakit mo hinawakan ang buhok ko nung sumusuka ako? Bakit hindi ka nadiri kahit nasukahan ko na ang pantalon mo, at natawa ka pa? Bakit mo pinunasan yung luha ko nung umiiyak ako dahil sa kanya? Bakit mo sinabi mo nang paulit-ulit na maganda ako nung paulit-ulit kitang tinanong kung pangit ba ako? Bakit ka nagpumilit na ihatid ako sa apartment? Why did you listen to every goddmned story I told without showing any sign of impatience? Why did you show me you care for me? Why did you give me so much attention? Sinabi ko naman sayong kapag nafall ako, I go crazy di ba? Bakit hindi ka nag-ingat?\r\nO baka nag-ingat ka, ako lang talaga ang tanga. O masyado lang talaga akong fragile that night. However, if anything, I know all the blame goes down to me. Ako naman ang na-fall. You were just being nice. Ako ang nahulog. Ako ang nagmisinterpret. Ako ang umasa.\r\nIsang buwan na ang nakalipas pero may hangover pa rin ako from that night. Hindi sa alak, kundi sayo. Pag pumupunta akong LB square, palingon-lingon ako sa paligid kasi umaasa akong nandun ka. Pero never pa ulit kitang nakita after that night. Ni hindi rin kita maadd sa facebook o mafollow sa twitter. Masyado nang traumatic yung nauna kong heartbreak and since malinaw naman na all those things were nothing to you because you didn\'t keep in touch, magmo-move on na lang ako ulit. Ayokong mag-risk na kausapin ka.\r\nI honestly thought you could help me end all my heartaches, turns out, you\'re just another goddmned problem. And I fcking hate it how I never learned a thing and fell for you. Even so, thank you for that night. I became happy for a while, and I enjoyed your company\r\nempigirl, 13, Socio, CAS'),
	(27, 'ano ko ba sasabihin sayong mahal kita? \r\nPareho na tayong graduating, ilang buwan na lang (sana), iiwan na natin ang UPLB, magkakaroon na tayo ng kanya kanyang buhay pagkatapos. Hindi ko alam ang gagawin ko kapag nangyari yun, hindi kita kayang mawala. Alam ko masyadong clingy kapag sinabi ko sayong sabay na lang tayong maghanap ng trabaho pero iba ang mga plano mo sa plano ko. Kahit sabihin nating we will keep in touch, hindi pa din natin sigurado kung mapapanindigan natin yun. Gusto kong umamin ng nararamdaman ko kasi ang tanga lang pero umaasa akong aamin ka din tapos magiging tayo. Kasi di ba, kapag naging tayo may kasiguraduhang hindi ka makakalimot? Ayaw ko ng kaibigan lang, kasi pag umaalis tayo ng university as friends, katulad ng mga high school friends ko eventually, magkakalimutan na tayo. Gusto kong magkaroon ng assurance na pagkatapos ng lahat ng magkaiba nating plano, babalik ka pa din sakin.\r\nPero hindi. Alam kong hindi. Kaya papahalagahan ko na lang ang bawat araw ng sem na ito kahit nagtethesis o madami ng exams, kasi, itong mga alaala ng huling semestre na lang ang panghahawakan ko kapag dumating na yung araw na isang numero na lang ako sa contacts mo.\r\nNatatakot, 2013, CAS'),
	(28, 'To miss firstandlast, una sa lahat hindi ka talaga panget. Crush kita... sobrang crush kita pero alam mo namang may GF ako, oh well X na nga pala kasi nabasa nya post mo and well, ilan lang talaga siguro kaming uncut sa elbi at tamag hinala si X. At linawin ko lang, ang ikli kasi ng post mo(wala masyado details) lasing tayo nun, ikaw mas lasing ka kasi hindi mo naaalala na sinabi kong uncut ako, hindi mo naalala na sinabi kong ""muka ka kasing virgin kaya baka hindi mo malaman ang difference ng uncut kasi yung GF ko sabi nya wala naman daw pala pinag-iba ang uncut actually mas nasarapan sya lalo na nung bj nya ako, parang kakaiba"" tapos ang sagot mo ""ay sorry, pang asawa lang ang virginiry ko"". Tapos may nangyari nga satin... Ano? Pwede na ba tayo?\r\nprouduncut, 2012, secret, GS'),
	(29, 'Me: *posted fb status* blah blah blah ..... #notodeathpenalty\r\nMe: Uy ok ba to? Tama naman grammar diba. Post ko na.\r\nFriend: lakaaaas. Eh ang favorite expression mo nga ""papatayin kita""\r\nMe: ay wow. Pag ba sinasabihan mo kong ""fuck you"", hinihindot mo ba ko?\r\nWag ako beshie.\r\nPapatayin ko kayong lahat, 2014, Dvm, CVM'),
	(30, 'The vindictive-bordering-arrogant attitude of some students here in the university forces me to hide my flaws even more and secretly condemn my personal stance on societal matters. They act & sound like they have the monopoly on thinking and being right, treating matters as if they have the all-seeing eye.\r\nHow do I even respond? It\'s as if they would use offensive sarcasm or even below-the-belt aggression if I\'d hit them with equally-confronting questions and statements. Help po\r\nLimbo, 2014, CAS'),
	(31, 'We\'re each others first.\r\nFirst kiss. First date. First everything.\r\nAnd now you want me to be your first..... you know.\r\nI kept holding back for the reason that it\'s wrong and we are deeply committed to our studies.\r\nWe almost.\r\nI don\'t want to have sex with you. Not even oral, not even just touching one anothers genitals.\r\nNo. Just no. Please I can\'t. Not yet. I\'m not ready for us to lose our virginity together.\r\nI feel like I could lose control anytime and something will happen that we would regret.\r\nYour kisses and hugs convinced me otherwise.\r\nI want to pleasure you, to give you something that no one would probably give to you.\r\nBut I don\'t think I should be giving it to you yet. Because we\'re still studying. Because I want what\'s best for us. I understand if you can\'t wait. Because I can\'t either.\r\nBut please, it\'s not worth the risk to do it. As much as I want to, I can\'t bring myself to do it.\r\nI\'m sorry if I can\'t. But no matter how long it takes, I\'m willing to wait. You are worth waiting for. You are worth my life. You are worth everything.\r\nI\'m sorry if I can\'t say it to you face-to-face or in chat or even while talking in the phone.\r\nIt\'s just, I don\'t want to disappoint you, or make you sad, or make you overthink.\r\nI\'m sorry.\r\nBut do know that I love you always. You\'re everything I could ask for.\r\nIt might sound like I might be in heat talking about those kinds of stuff with you. Inside, I feel guilty and wrong about it.\r\nLet\'s be patient, give it a few years and a marriage and I promise I will give it to you.\r\nI can wait. I\'m a patient person. We\'ll always have each other.\r\nDandelion, 14, CAS'),
	(32, 'Nakalabas na ako sa friendzone nung umamin ako sa\'yo pero somehow iniisip ko pa rin na baka pinupursue mo lang ako kasi alam mo na yung feelings ko. Kasi alam nating pareho ngayon na for the past 5 years na magkasama tayo, I was literally invisible to you to the point na wala kang maalalang memories natin, samantalang ako madami, madami akong tinetreasure na moments na magkasama tayo at nag-uusap lang ng ilang oras sa sasakyan, sa tabing dagat, sa sala ng bahay niyo at sa simbahan.\r\nHindi kita sinusumbatan kung hindi mo ako nakikita before kasi ako naman yung umasa, normal naman kasi na umasa kapag may feelings ka for a person. Logically dapat wag umasa but truth is it is inevitable. Lahat ng nagmamahal mas sumasaya kapag minamahal pabalik, and we all want that happiness. Pero pwede pala talaga yun, yung asado ka for 5 years sa isang bagay na wala naman pala.\r\nNasasaktan pa ako nun tuwing may ikukuwento ka sa akin na crush mo, at some point inisip ko nun pinapaselos mo lang ako pero hindi pala eh kasi nga wala lang naman ako sa\'yo, not even a close friend to start with. Sobra akong affected noon nung may pinursue kang girl pagkatapos kong hindi magparamdam ng 2 months. It was kinda funny kasi for the past two years, I blamed myself for ""letting you go"", na kasalanan ko na napunta ka sa kanya kasi hindi kita pinahalagahan. Hindi ako nagparamdam kasi I was testing kung hanggang kailan mo kaya maghintay, hahaha eh hindi ka naman pala maghihintay kasi wala ka namang hinihintay. Hindi ko nga alam kung naaalala mo pa yun eh kasi when I backtracked, I saw that during those same time na akala ko may thing tayo, meron na din palang closeness na nabubuo sainyo nung isang girl which I failed to see kasi I had my own fantasy of the idea of you and me. Akala ko kasi noon dahil bigla kang naging chummy after my 18th birthday and we were talking spontaneously everyday till dawn, we were already having a thing, akala ko lang pala. I was so caught up in my dream that I never realized that maybe you\'re not into me. Totoo naman kasi, you\'re not the torpe kind of guy, you tell someone if you like them, which you never did to me before but you told me, six months after I confessed to you.\r\nKung susundan ang plot ng movies dapat hindi na kita ""balikan."" It\'s the usual plot, girl loves boy first, but boy doesn\'t see her worth. She moves on, only then will boy see her worth but she has already moved on. Let\'s have all the feelings FLIPPED. To make things complicated dapat hindi na kita ine-entertain ngayon, dapat nakamove-on na ako, ideally dapat may other boy na ako na nandyan para sa akin at para magselos ka. Pero hindi ito pelikula, never ako naghold ng grudge sa\'yo when you told me na wala naman talaga kasi I still value our friendship. I was happy na nakakausap na kita noon na klaro sa akin na wala na and walang inaasahang kapalit kasi tinanggal ko lahat ng romantic feelings when we interact. Hindi ko kinailangan na magkaroon ng other guy on the process of moving on kasi I never had the need for validation from another guy, though there was a time na ginusto ko rin naman but I moved on on my own. But I hear my friends\' voice say, ""Nagmove on nga ba?""\r\nI moved on for quite some time. I knew my place in your life and stayed there and never wished to go beyond that but I knew that I still had some feelings esp when I think of someone else but it\'s you that I see in my mind.I did my best na umiwas pero nung muli tayong nagkita, civil pa rin naman pero umiwas ako, umiwas ako pero umasang kakausapin mo ako. Ganun kasi tayo for the past five years, asiwa ako tapos lalapit ka then mag-uusap na tayo. Some said I was just having withdrawal syndrome, for the past years masyado akong nasanay sa set-up nating dalawa kaya hinahanap ko pa rin kahit ako yung pumipigil. It\'s not that I haven\'t moved on, it\'s just that it has become a habit amd habits take time to break but when the time to break it has come, nagpasabog ka bigla, you said you\'re gonna pursue me.\r\nI was shocked, a bit. I knew this was a possibility but never really thought of how to react because though I knew this might happen when I came home but I never really entertained the idea of us anymore. \r\nBut now here I am, writing this and somehow yes I am accommodating your pursuit. Your efforts are undoubtedly sincere but still your initial intentions make me think. Still, I take risks but I don\'t feel risking anything at all, all I know is that I\'m happy when I\'m with you. I don\'t want to deprive myself of that happiness anymore.\r\nBtw before I confessed to you, you asked me if I\'m drunk. I said, ""No, I\'m not drunk, but I like you.""\r\nCarson with a different ending?, 2013, CAS'),
	(33, 'GAPANG\r\nPara dun sa roommate ko nang dalawang taon! Utang na loob naman friend! Afford mo naman ang shampoo pampatanggal ng kuto. Tyagaan nga lang sa pag suyod at pag tiris pero maawa ka naman sa amin ples. Tuwing bakasyon feel na feel ng nanay ko paghinguto sa kin mas namiss niya pa yata yung pinasa mong alaga sakin kesa sa akin na anak niya. Tapos ang sarap sa feeling na fresh buhok mo bago mag pasukan kasi walang nagapang sa ulo mo. Pero heto na naman ate! Dalawang linggo palang tayong pumapasok at magkasama sa kwarto ito na naman guuurl ramdam ko na naman sila! Alam ko namang alam mo na madami kang alaga so please lang obosen mo na sila. Tuwing pasukan nalang ba ganito? Ayoko na ples huhuhuhuhu ang hirap mag aral kapag may nagapang sa ulo (TT)\r\nSuyudanTayo, 15, CEAT'),
	(34, 'Dumadami na yung accounts na Iska, Isko, Pegaraw, Mariang Banga, ano pa ba? Hahaha. Minsan nakakaannoy kasi mainstream na pero okay lang! Tuloy niyo lang! Pampagoodvibes!\r\nAnyway, gusto ko lang i-commend silang lahat kasi shet dami nilang time! Tsaka ambabait pa. Lalo na si Iskang Elbi, shet bes thank you sa posts at random messages mo. Sobrang ramdam kong mabait yung taong nasa likod ng account mo. Stay lovely po ?\r\nSana mameet ko kayong lahat in person! I support you all!\r\nInvader, 14, BS Pogi, CAS'),
	(35, 'Hey guys! I\'ve been struggling with my boyfriend lately. We\'ve been a couple for some time now and he knows who I really am. You see, I was his first girlfriend and he wanted to have all his ""first"" with me. The problem is that he wasn\'t my first boyfriend. Before we became a couple, I clarified everything about me that might be a hindrance someday. I told him who I was and what I was then. I was up front honest. I told him all the flaws that I see in me. I told him that I had past relationships before. I told him that I had been into rehab due to my social anxiety order. And...I told him that I wasn\'t a virgin anymore and that if he couldn\'t handle it I\'d understand. I mean who wants to be with someone who\'s wrong in the head and not a virgin, right? I was broken then but he need not to fix me. If he can\'t handle how jacked up my life is then it\'s fine. I never felt normal, anyways. I can\'t force him to accept me because I couldn\'t even accept my self. I was crying then. But he told me he didn\'t mind. He liked me for who I am and that\'s that. Who I was isn\'t who I am.... Blah blah blah\r\nSo yeah. We became a couple and I was happy for most days. I felt normal around him and that I wasn\'t alone anymore. I was happy and content.\r\nMonths passed by and and the whole honeymoon period ended. Our fights became often and it was always about similar things. It became a cycle. He would always bring up our past arguments and my past. Like how he hates my ex and wishes to kill him. "" how could you date someone so ugly?"", he\'d ask often. ""How could I be so depressed from time to time"" and ""why the hell would you have sex with him?, bat sila nauna?"" ""I am number four!!!"" those were the things I\'d often hear from him and it always broke me a little.\r\nI wanted to leave the relationship but I couldn\'t. I deeply cared about him and I think na maybe after a few more months he\'ll realize his mistake and make up for it. I was always honest and I\'d tell him how I felt.\r\nIn the past few months we had less arguments and I was glad we survived. I mean we barely dragged ourselves to our one year mark. I thought okay na.. However, a few days ago we had argument and it lead to another argument with me not being a virgin. I understood that some of guys want \' em young and fresh but that doesn\'t mean that someone who had intercourse is equivalent to a pair of used shoes. There\'s more to a person than that. I tried to act like I\'m better than that but the truth is I felt really bad. I feel like garbage and decay. I\'m useless and should be thrown out. I\'m starting to give in and I couldn\'t shake the thought of being unaccepted by someone who made me feel normal and loved once.\r\nP.S. sana ma post \'to. I\'m losing it. I want this pain to go away. I want to go away. I want go bye bye.\r\nDiptera:Tabanidae , 14 , CVM'),
	(36, 'I just witnessed something that I think I should have not.\r\nI happen to have free time so I sat here and there.\r\nThere\'s an old professor reaching his phone out to probably get some signal. After getting a signal, this professor gets inside a room while talking to someone through the phone.\r\nA few moments later, a young student comes in and to my surprise, he locks the mothereffin door.\r\nI mean, would that really be necessary? Come on something\'s really suspicious about that.\r\nFurthermore, after the guy went out, he looked really messed up than when he came in. I\'m really bothered about this and to think that the prof looks so old and probably is gay due to his actions from before.\r\nWell, who cares? Maybe it\'s due to old people having better skills? Or perhaps he has fetishes that I could not possibly comprehend? Or kinailangan lang talaga niyang kumapit sa patalim to satisfy his daily financial/acads needs?\r\nThis post is so damn judgmental. Malay mo naman nagaaral sila and they don\'t want anyone to disturb them kaya naglock sila.\r\nAnyways, maybe I\'ll always stay in that spot during my free time. Wait for updates. Nah haha just kidding it\'s so gross.\r\nObservantVullaby, 2015, BUILDING WITH THE MOST UNREFINED COMFORT ROOM, CAS'),
	(37, 'I was diagnosed with cancer.\r\nNung nalaman ko, parang ayaw ko na lang talaga mabuhay. Yung dating sobrang excited akong pumasok, mag aral, makipag socialize with friends, ngayon ayaw ko nalang bumangon. Para saan pa? Mamamatay rin lang naman ako. Everyday na nararamdaman kong humihina ako, lalo ako nawawalan ng gana. Medyo active kasi akong tao. Mahilig ako sa sports, mag gym, at sobrang dami ko talagang energy para sa mga bagay bagay. Ngayon, wala na. Di ko na magawa lahat ng nagagawa ko noon. Ni pag ngiti di ko na kaya.\r\nMy family has always been there for me through thick and thin. Pero parang ayaw ko na silang pahirapan. Madami akong pangarap noon pero ngayon naglaho nalang ng parang bula ang lahat kasi alam kong di na ako sasablay, magkakatrabaho, magpapakasal, magkakaanak, magkakapamilya ng sarili ko.\r\nI saw how Jam Sebastian suffered. Ang tagal nun. Ayoko nun. Ayoko.\r\nFeeling ko marami magccomment sa confession ko na ang arte ko, na di pa naman stage 4 kung makainarte ako parang wala ng bukas, na maraming ibang tao na mas malala pa piniproblema... pero sorry, di kasi ako sanay sa ganito. Like I said, active akong tao. Kaya sobrang hirap para sakin yung feeling na mabilis na mapagod, at yung alam kong may sakit ako.\r\nI have thoughts of ending my life already. Dun din naman kasi patutunguhan nun. Ayaw ko na pahirapan pamilya ko. Ayaw ko na sayangin pa pera nila sa mga mangyayaring pagpapagamot sa future. Ayaw ko na lumaban. Oo, marami akong tao na masasaktan kasi nga bibo kid ako at marami akong kaibigan. Pero mas mahihirapan lang sila kung unti unti nila akong nakikitang nagiging lantang gulay.\r\nAlam ko sobrang nonsense ng pag confess dito pero kailangan ko lang ilabas lahat ng nasa utak ko ngayon. Ayoko na kasi makipag usap kahit kanino. Di na ako lumalabas ng kwarto. Ilang araw na akong absent sa mga klase ko. I do not see any light in the tunnel anymore.\r\nBlack&Decker, 2014, CAS'),
	(38, 'Sobrang hirap ba maging sensitive?\r\nPara sa kapitbahay naming org, onting hiya naman po. 1am na, nagtatawanan pa kayo ng malakas. Di ko naman kayo masaway kasi feeling ko mga lasing na kayo. Pero tama ba na magiinuman kayo ng mid-week? Paano yung mga kapitbahay nyo na gusto magpahinga? Paano yung mga nag-aral kasi may exams? Onting hiya naman diyan oh. Pakitandaan na nasa isang apartment compound kayo. Hindi lang kayo ang nakatira dito.\r\nTapos magwoworkshop kayo, pero hindi naman kayo maglilinis ng mga kalat nyo? Tapos liliparin ng hangin sa hall yung mga kalat nyo? Kasi naglilinis yung mga caretaker daily kaya ganon? Feeling nyo may janitor kayo kaya wala nang hiya hiya sa kalat? Tatlo org ko pero never kami umalis sa lugar kung saan kami nagworkshop ng hindi malinis yung lugar.\r\nSobrang nag-iba ang tingin ko sa org nyo. Nakakahiya na dala nyo ang pangalan nito. Pasensiya na at nagrarant ako, pakitandaan naman sana natin na kapag parte ka ng isang organisasyon, dala mo ang ngalan nito kahit saan. Kung ano ang gawin nyo, maa-associate ito sa org nyo. Medyo umakto naman tayong professional diba?\r\nSalty Neighbor, 2013, CVM'),
	(39, 'HINDI ITO KALANDIAN PERO PUTA MEDYO NAPUPUNO NA AKO I NEED A FUCKING ADVICE ????????\r\nHanggang saan ba ang limitations ng pag iingay when it comes to dormitory/ apartment kapag sleeping time na???!!! Specifically roommates??? ????????\r\nPuta hala sige mag ingay ka/kayo kapag maaga pa WALA AKONG PAKE SASABAYAN KO PA KAYO. Pero pucha naman pag sleeping time na sleeping time na oh!! You know how hard and crucial it is to function well sa classes kapag kulang ka sa tulog, diba??? Tangina lang roomie, naalala mo pa ba nung exam week mo? Nung gabi ka na nags start mag aral tapos aabutin ng madaling araw(kahit marami ka naman vacant sa hapon)?? Kapag pucha lakas mo maka volume habang nanonood ng videos na bigay ng prof mo for exam tapos tutulugan mo lang at mapapaiyak na lang ako as i checked the clock kasi it is already 2AM AND I AM FUCKING WIDE AWAKE BC OF YOUR NOISE?? KULANG NA LANG BATUHIN KITA NG WALL CLOCK PARA MAGISING KA AT MATAHIMIK NA YANG VIDEOS MO. Kapag manonood ka ng movies at medyo malakas pa volume. Ok lang naman sakin eh pero kapag naman 11-12 na awat na tayo PLZ Or mag earphones ka pahiramin pa kita. Sinasabihan naman kita minsan pero inuulit mo lang din makalipas ang ilang panahon. Minsan di na lang ako nakibo at hinahayaan ko na lang mapuyat ako para wala na lang issue pero pucha naman di ko naman kaya na poreber na lang ganto (kasi walang ganun ulul).\r\nNao off na ko sayo minsan. Minsan mababalitaan ko pa sa friends mo na late or absent ka sa klase mo kahit di naman ganun ka aga ???? Ano ba talaga priority mo sa life? Maging sensitive ka naman at di yung parang walang muwang palagi\r\nPakisabi naman sakin ako pa rin ba mali????Sawang sawa na ko mag adjust.\r\n((Admin pa post naman please nagbabasa yun dito at para narin matamaan yung ibang roomies diyan na mahilig mameste ng tulog))\r\nAGIT NA AKO, 14, Course ng magaganda, CHE'),
	(40, 'Hello, sino sa inyo yung batch 10 (or older hehehe sorry na) na nag-apply for extension at approved? Gusto ko lang malaman kung ano yung meron kayo na wala sa jowakels ko. Ilang weeks na kaming stressed dahil sa disapproval ng extension niya. :(\r\nNabalitaan kasi namin na merong mga batch 10, 09, 08 na 60+ or 50+ units pa, pero tinanggap naman yung extension. Bakit yung jowa ko, 42 units nalang, dinisapprove pa. Di naman siya dismissed. Di rin probi. (May isang bagsak at isang 4 oki) Tapos kasi, a year ago, nareadmit siya, and tinanggap naman ni chancy yung nasa plan of study niya na 2 years pa kailangan niya. (So bale ngayon 1 year nalang di ba 2-1=1 tama ba) So far, hindi naman mageextend further, like hindi naman nadagdagan ng sem. Ano yun, ""I change my mind. Ayaw ko na pala sayo"" ganern?\r\nNaka-4 na appeal na pero lahat disapproved. Samantalang yung ibang may kachikahan sa OC, kahit mas panget standing keribels lang approved pa rin. Tapos interview siya ni Sir A***** dun sa anooooo, sa taas ng lib para sabihin na disapproved ulit yung appeal sa OC. Nung binring up niya yung tungkol dun sa ibang mas madami pang units pero approved, sabi daw sa kanya hindi naman tinitignan sa OC yung grades/standing. Sa OVCAA lang daw yun. (Eh kaya nga nag-appeal sa OC kasi disapproved sa OVCAA. Pero yung case na binanggit ay sa OC rin naman inakyat yun at inapprove nila. So ano basis nung pag-approve dun mars? Pagandahan ng essay ganern?)\r\n18 units yung jowakels ko this sem pero masasayang dahil ayaw na nila iapprove :( grabe naman sila sa nagbabagong buhay ;( tapos unfair pa :(\r\n(Hi babe. Kapit lang. Love you!)\r\nShaninani, 9, CAS');
